long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en_GB,en_US,e:
This extension allows you to access Google's App Launcher right from the chrome toolbar. This way, you don't need to open a new tab or browse to a google website to access it.

This extension needs permission to https://mail.google.com/ in order to display the app launcher in a popup.
